    "Meta-learning is a scenario when one solves many machine learning tasks simulataneously, and the objective is to improve this learning process for yet-to-come tasks.",
    "A popular formalization (but not the only one possible) is:",
    "• each task t ∈ {1,.",
    ", T } corresponds to a probability distribution P t.",
    "The P t 's are i.i.d. from some P."
